OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FA Scottish charity providing food to
OL,8,Fchildren in Haiti has launched an
OL,9,Furgent appeal for support as the
OL,10,Fcountry grapples with escalating gang
OL,11,Fviolence and its worst hunger crisis.
OL,13,FAccording to the World Food Programme,
OL,14,Fmore than half the population of the
OL,15,FCaribbean country ` some 5.7 million
OL,16,Fpeople ` is experiencing acute levels
OL,17,Fof hunger, including at least one
OL,18,Fmillion children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMary's Meals, which provides school
OL,8,Fmeals to children in 16 countries,
OL,9,Fsaid many children are being lured
OL,10,Finto joining armed gangs by the
OL,11,Fpromise of food.
OL,13,FThe charity also said armed conflict
OL,14,Fis intensifying in the absence of a
OL,15,Ffunctional government and that more
OL,16,Fthan 1.4 million people are displaced,
OL,17,Fhalf of whom are children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FIt said gangs control 90% of the
OL,8,Fcapital city Port-Au-Prince, with
OL,9,Fviolence spreading to areas of the
OL,10,Fcountry that were previously
OL,11,Fconsidered safe.
OL,13,FEmmline Toussaint, main coordinator of
OL,14,Fthe charity's school feeding programme
OL,15,Fin Haiti, said: "Gangs are always
OL,16,Ftrying to target children because they
OL,17,Fare most vulnerable, most in need of
OL,18,Fassistance.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"You cannot get out once you get in a
OL,8,Fgang. It's either you die, or your
OL,9,Ffamily dies, or you stay in.
OL,11,F"We've already lost those aged 15 to
OL,12,F30. That's why we need to work more
OL,13,Fwith those children aged three to 14.
OL,15,F"They are the ones that we should
OL,16,Ffocus on, those little ones. They need
OL,17,Fus to guide them differently."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMary's Meals reaches children by
OL,8,Fworking with local partners, who have
OL,9,Fadapted their delivery plans to keep
OL,10,Freaching as many schools as possible.
OL,12,FThe charity said in schools where it
OL,13,Foperates, children have a reason to go
OL,14,Fto class and have the energy to
OL,15,Fconcentrate during lessons ` staying
OL,16,Fconnected and, for a short time at
OL,17,Fleast, feeling safe.
OL,19,FMore than half of Haiti's population
OL,20,Fis younger than 25, and one in five
OL,21,Fare aged between 15 and 24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
