CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMagnus MacFarlane-Barrow founded
OL,8,FMary's Meals from a shed in the
OL,9,FScottish Highlands more than 20 years
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,F"I knew from my visits that, from the
OL,13,Fbeginning, Haiti would be an extremely
OL,14,Fdifficult place for us to work," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"But I had no doubt that it was
OL,18,Fsomewhere we should be providing
OL,19,FMary's Meals.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@`O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"What I could have never imagined is
OL,8,Fthat, 20 years later, the situation
OL,9,Fwould be even more terrible.
OL,11,F"Poverty, hunger, and disruption still
OL,12,Fstand in the way of children and their
OL,13,Feducation.
OL,15,F"Yet there are signs of hope ` a child
OL,16,Fsmiling in school where they feel safe
OL,17,Fand receive a meal, and teachers who
OL,18,Fkeep showing up for their classes with
OL,19,Fremarkable courage.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"Our meals help children to stay in
OL,8,Fschool, and we will keep doing all we
OL,9,Fcan to ensure those we serve can
OL,10,Fcontinue to depend on us."
OL,12,FMs Toussaint said: "The situation in
OL,13,FHaiti has long been difficult but I
OL,14,Fcannot think of a time when things
OL,15,Fhave been so desperate.
OL,17,F"I remember my own childhood. You
OL,18,Fcould go out in your yard and play
OL,19,Fwith others your age.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@ZO]tD@TOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"Now, if a day passes without hearing
OL,8,Fany shootings, it's a great day. But
OL,9,Fshootings are every day, every single
OL,10,Fday."
OL,12,FMary's Meals said together with three
OL,13,Flocal partners it is now operating in
OL,14,Fone of the most challenging and risky
OL,15,Fsituations it has ever faced.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAs well as the price of food and fuel
OL,8,Fincreasing, it said the safe
OL,9,Ftransportation of food is also costing
OL,10,Fmore than ever as suppliers have to
OL,11,Fuse longer but currently safer routes
OL,12,Fto avoid the gang-controlled main
OL,13,Fhighways.
OL,15,FThe charity has issued an urgent
OL,16,Fappeal for donations to help it
OL,17,Fprovide nutrition to children in a
OL,18,Fsafe place of learning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773630202
OL,3,CCharity feeding children in Haiti
OL,4,Cappeals for support amid severe hunger
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"Mary's Meals urgently needs support
OL,8,Fto keep its promise to the children it
OL,9,Fserves in Haiti and show them that
OL,10,Fthere is hope beyond the violence,"
OL,11,Fthe charity said.
OL,13,F"Right now, your gift does more than
OL,14,Fprovide food ` it helps children stay
OL,15,Fin school, where they can learn and
OL,16,Fgrow into the leaders who will
OL,17,Ftransform Haiti's future."
OL,19,FTo donate visit the website,
OL,20,Fmarysmeals.org.uk.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@cO]uD@AOUyD@ZO]
